<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Until <date date="1997-11-10">Nov. 10, 1997</date>, by <ref href="/us/pl/105/69">Pub. L. 105–69</ref>, <date date="1997-11-09">Nov. 9, 1997</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/111/1454">111 Stat. 1454</ref>.</p>
