<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="miscellaneous" id="iddb5e3137-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Financial Assistance to the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/93/450/s1">Pub. L. 93–450, § 1</ref>, <date date="1974-10-18">Oct. 18, 1974</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/88/1368">88 Stat. 1368</ref>, provided in part that the Bank shall not authorize any financial assistance to the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics during the life of <ref href="/us/pl/93/450">Pub. L. 93–450</ref>, which extended the termination date from <date date="1974-10-15">Oct. 15, 1974</date>, to <date date="1974-11-30">Nov. 30, 1974</date>.</p>
